title: International Cup 2025 dates set
content: The 2025 Lansdowne International Cup will be held from Oct.17 to Oct 18th. Check out the [tournament format](#format) and view the [complete schedule](#schedule) for more details.

title: Member Registration Now Open
content: Registration for International Cup 2025 is now open for members! [Join our member area](/members/) to register for the tournament and access exclusive content. Learn more [about the competition](#about).
